						               													<description>Description from the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Calling all ACME agents to figure out Where in the World is Carmen Sandiego?!?! Can you handle this challenge, Gumshoes? It looks like Carmen&amp;rsquo;s gang has pulled another caper.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the Where in the World is Carmen Sandiego? Card Game, you will be on a top-secret mission to recover the greatest treasures known to mankind &amp;ndash; The Grand Canyon, the Statue of Liberty&amp;rsquo;s Torch, and more. Get ready to jet set across the globe. Your assignment is to apprehend Carmen Sandiego, track the location of her hideout, and determine which loot she stole.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gumshoes, your goal is to eliminate as many Loot, Location, and Henchman Cards as possible by finding the matching Loot and Location Cards. This will ultimately lead you to Carmen Sandiego and one Loot-Location Card set.  Just like any good detective, you must be vigilant in collecting evidence to solve this mystery. In your Top-Secret Evidence Journals, keep track of your fellow Gumshoes&amp;rsquo; cards by writing down their Location and Loot Cards and whether they&amp;rsquo;re at the top, center, or bottom of their piles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you do not know where Carmen is but you think you&amp;rsquo;ve discovered matching Loot and Location Cards, call out &amp;ldquo;I have a warrant!&amp;rdquo; Once you zero in on Carmen&amp;rsquo;s location, you must declare &amp;ldquo;I have a warrant for Carmen&amp;rsquo;s arrest.&amp;rdquo; The first Gumshoe to make a Loot-Location match and successfully reveal Carmen wins the game. But beware, if you make an incorrect accusation, Carmen can escape!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
